dct_description_sm: Published at Washington D.C. Oct. 1933 by the U.S. Coast and Geodetic Survey ; R.S. Patton, Director.
Depths shown by soundings; relief by contours and spot heights.
Shows coast, small islands, gulches, buildings.
Textual descriptions, such as "breakers," and "sugar cane."
